assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Toumei Co., Ltd. offers telecommunications services in Japan. The company provides optical collaboration services for small and medium enterprises; offers Internet services, content, and support services; and creates Websites. It also offers power, eco, and web solutions; information terminal equipment sales/security services; office supplies mail order services; and insurance agency services by visiting shop. In addition, the company provides optical internet and telephone, web consulting, LP site production, internet providers, domain services, network security, commercial air conditioner and refrigerator, LED lighting, diagnosis, application tools, cloud cash registers, digital signage, water server, business phone, MFP, PC, network HDD and cameras, SMS, cloud backup, device warranty, remote support, data recovery, terrestrial digital broadcasting, e-magazine, wi-fi, IVR, anshin HACCP, office DX support, electricity and gas, and website production services. The company was formerly known as Tomei Mie and changed its name to Tomei Co., Ltd. in 2001. Tomei Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Yokkaichi, Japan.
